config GPIO_VIRTIO
	bool "VIRTIO GPIO driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_VIRTIO_GPIO_ENABLED
	select VIRTIO
	help
	  Enable driver for VIRTIO GPIO devices.

	  Every operation is a round trip to the virtio device, so the GPIO API
	  can only be used from a thread, including from the interrupt callbacks
	  fired by this driver.
